                        <div class="tab-pane" id="profile1">
                            <div class="faq_1ri p-4 bg-white shadow_box">
                                <h5 class="col_oran">Pricing</h5>
                                <p>
                                    Transparency and fairness are the cornerstones of our pricing model. All ticket prices on our platform are determined by the cinema providers and are displayed clearly with no hidden fees. We add a nominal convenience fee to support the operational costs of hosting a seamless booking service, including server management, customer support, and software development.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Factors influencing ticket prices:
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Theatre category (Multiplex or Single Screen)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Location (Urban, Tier 1/2/3 cities)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Show time (Morning, Matinee, Evening, Late Night)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Seat type (Regular, VIP, Premium Recliner, Gold Class)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Screen format (2D, 3D, 4DX, IMAX)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Special shows (Premieres, Private screenings)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    During the checkout process, users are provided with a complete price breakdown including base fare, taxes (GST), and convenience charges. Our interface also highlights ongoing offers, bank discounts, and promo code options, allowing users to make the most of their bookings.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    We also offer bulk pricing and group booking rates for educational institutions, corporate outings, and event tie-ins. Please reach out to our customer support team for more details on these specialized rates.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="tab-pane" id="profile2">
                            <div class="faq_1ri p-4 bg-white shadow_box">
                                <h5 class="col_oran">Booking</h5>
                                <p>
                                    Our booking process is designed for simplicity and flexibility, offering a hassle-free experience regardless of whether you're using a mobile device or a desktop.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6> Step-by-Step Booking: </h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    1. Search Movies: Use filters like language, genre, release date, and rating.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    2. Choose a Cinema: Select a theatre based on proximity, showtimes, and amenities.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    3. Pick a Show: Check showtimes by date and view the real-time seating chart.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    4.Seat Selection: Choose your seats interactively; color-coded for availability and pricing.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    5. Review Booking: View your ticket summary, selected seats, and pricing details.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    6. Apply Offers: Redeem coupons or promo codes.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    7. Proceed to Payment: Complete the booking using your preferred payment method.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6> Once payment is confirmed, you receive: </h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * A digital ticket (PDF and in-app)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Email confirmation
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * SMS alert with QR code
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6>You can also: </h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Share bookings with friends
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Download tickets for offline access
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Add the event to your calendar

                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

