                                <h5 class="col_oran">Payment</h5>
                                <p>
                                    Security, reliability, and flexibility guide our payment infrastructure. We have partnered with trusted payment gateways to offer a seamless and safe transaction process for all users.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6>Available payment methods:</h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Debit/Credit Cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, RuPay)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Net Banking (All major Indian banks)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * UPI (Paytm, Google Pay, PhonePe, BHIM)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Wallets (Paytm Wallet, Amazon Pay, MobiKwik)
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Gift Cards, Movie Vouchers, Loyalty Points
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    All payment processes are encrypted using SSL protocols and comply with RBI standards. Payment failure handling, instant refund initiation, and retry options are available for users who face issues during checkout.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Your financial data is never stored or shared. Our systems log anonymized transaction identifiers for your account history and refund tracking.
                                </p>
                            </div>
