                        <div class="tab-pane" id="profile4">
                            <div class="faq_1ri p-4 bg-white shadow_box">
                                <h5 class="col_oran">Cancellation and Refunds Statement</h5>
                                <p>
                                    Life is unpredictable, and we get it. Our cancellation and refund policies are crafted to be fair and user-centric, keeping both cinema rules and user needs in mind.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6>Cancellation Guidelines:</h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * You can cancel your booking directly through the website or app.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Cancellations are accepted up to a defined cut-off before showtime (typically 1–3 hours).
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Refund amount depends on the theatre’s cancellation policy.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6>Refund Policy:</h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Convenience fees are usually non-refundable.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Refunds are credited to the original payment method within 5–7 business days.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Refunds for cancelled shows or technical failures are processed automatically.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <h6>Ineligible Cases:</h6>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Missed shows
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Partially used tickets
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    * Showtimes that have already started
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Users are advised to check theatre-specific policies on the booking summary page. We also provide real-time updates if any changes occur in the theatre's schedule.
                                </p>
                            </div>
